snippet.textDisplay: Honestly, I don't feel there's any new sound or beats in this song. Also, I would prefer to hear more of Abdul Wabab Bugti than Kaifi Khalil. There's a different tonal quality in Abdul Wabab's voice than the other vocal that was given preference. Also, the camera work just distracts me from the sound of the song. However, it's me, an avid coke Studio fan who looks forward to seasons every year right from when Rohail Hyatt started to compose. And it's my humble request, please do upload the subtitles with the release of the song, it helps people like us. I hope the next song hits home. Till then, love to all the listeners.
snippet.textOriginal: Honestly, I don't feel there's any new sound or beats in this song. Also, I would prefer to hear more of Abdul Wabab Bugti than Kaifi Khalil. There's a different tonal quality in Abdul Wabab's voice than the other vocal that was given preference. Also, the camera work just distracts me from the sound of the song. However, it's me, an avid coke Studio fan who looks forward to seasons every year right from when Rohail Hyatt started to compose. And it's my humble request, please do upload the subtitles with the release of the song, it helps people like us. I hope the next song hits home. Till then, love to all the listeners.
